It is the third time this season Villa have been hit with such a charge following similar incidents in the matches with Spurs on November 2 and Manchester United on December 20.

The incidents have resulted in £20,000 and £30,000 fines respectively.

Leicester beat Villa 1-0 thanks to Paul Konchesky's goal on the stroke of half-time.

